"""Test Missing Opening Bracket"""
D = {'color': 'brown', 'animal': 'aardvark'}
s = 'How now color}} cow.'
with self.assertRaises(MyTemplateError):
    render(s, D)
s = 'How now color}} {{animal}}.'
with self.assertRaises(MyTemplateError):
    render(s, D)
s = 'How now {{color}} animal}}.'
with self.assertRaises(MyTemplateError):
    render(s, D)
